

modified hccontrol with hcscanner

Waitman Gobble <ns@waitman.net>


hcscanner connects to up to 3 bluetooth devices and scans for up to 1000 new BD Addresses in range 


# make

# make clean



# ./hcscanner
        ubt0hci BD_ADDR: 00:1b:dc:06:5c:b5
        ubt0hci BD_ADDR: cc:6d:a0:ba:73:e8
        ubt0hci BD_ADDR: 78:e8:b6:76:6f:1e
        ubt1hci BD_ADDR: 00:1b:dc:06:ae:4c
        ubt2hci BD_ADDR: 00:1b:dc:06:94:d3
        ubt0hci BD_ADDR: 00:1a:7d:da:71:13
        ubt0hci BD_ADDR: c8:84:47:22:38:20

-r switch turns on RSSI scanning.

# ./hcscanner -r

        ubt0hci BD_ADDR: cc:6d:a0:ba:73:e8
        ubt0hci BD_ADDR: 00:1a:7d:da:71:13
        ubt0hci BD_ADDR: 00:1b:dc:06:5c:b5
